01:08:08,550 --> 01:08:10,279
Sweetie, what's...?

951
01:08:10,451 --> 01:08:12,351
It's locked, she's mopping.

952
01:08:12,520 --> 01:08:14,112
Try the...

953
01:08:14,289 --> 01:08:17,190
