969
01:10:28,356 --> 01:10:30,324
Oh.

970
01:10:31,359 --> 01:10:33,224
This is not nonfat.

971
01:10:33,561 --> 01:10:34,994
Oh.

972
01:10:35,163 --> 01:10:39,190
I love your books. Your shit's brilliant.

973
01:10:39,367 --> 01:10:40,959
Cathy?

974
01:10:41,969 --> 01:10:44,665
- You seem drunk.
- Little bit.

