01:11:40,328 --> 01:11:41,590
To fall in love.

990
01:11:43,131 --> 01:11:46,498
- What? That's corny, right?
- No.

991
01:11:46,667 --> 01:11:50,626
No, no, it's... It's just very honest.

992
01:11:51,672 --> 01:11:55,870
I don't think that I've heard
anybody say that in a very long time.

993
01:11:56,411 --> 01:11:57,742
Well...

994
01:11:59,680 --> 01:12:03,013
So Louise from St. Louis,
I just have one more question.

995
01:12:03,184 --> 01:12:04,208
Okay.

996
01:12:04,419 --> 01:12:06,751
How does an unemployed girl
with three roommates...

997
01:12:06,921 --> 01:12:09,446
