01:13:23,030 --> 01:13:27,160
MAGDA: I lived here before.
It used to be all-Ukrainian area.

1017
01:13:27,335 --> 01:13:28,393
Mm-hm.

1018
01:13:28,569 --> 01:13:30,264
A U-Haul.

1019
01:13:31,005 --> 01:13:32,404
Coming or going?

1020
01:13:33,074 --> 01:13:36,134
- Going. Oh, boy. I'm gonna check it out.
- Okay.

1021
01:13:36,310 --> 01:13:37,299
Wait down here, okay?

1022
01:13:37,478 --> 01:13:42,677
<i>And there in old Ukrainia,</i>
<i>Miranda found her new apartment.</i>

1023
01:13:44,385 --> 01:13:46,853
CARRIE: "And there they remained
